articles.title: An American tourist has died following an attack near Germany’s Neuschwanstein Castle - CNN
articles.description: A 21-year-old American woman died after being assaulted and pushed down a slope by an American man near one of Germany’s most popular tourist sights, Neuschwanstein Castle, in Bavaria, according to local police.
